The '''Free People''' were a group on [[Wayland/Legends|Wayland]] who resisted the invasion of their homeworld by the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. The Free People was organized of the locals of Wayland including [[Human/Legends|Humans]], [[Myneyrsh]] and the [[Psadan]]s. Their leader was [[Txer]] and aided [[Uldir Lochett]] when he came to Wayland in search of [[Klin-Fa Gi]].

